@remote_operations_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### List available boot entries
GET {{remote_operations_HostAddress}}/reboot/entries
Accept: application/json

###

### Reboot into the current/default OS
POST {{remote_operations_HostAddress}}/reboot
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Reboot into a specific OS entry (replace ID with one from /reboot/entries)
POST {{remote_operations_HostAddress}}/reboot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetEntryId": "{00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000}"
}

###
